  "3056580": {
    "name": "桃花源物语：建造小镇",
    "steam_appid": 3056580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/fb50908cf5418cc8193ff90607ea6676.avif?t=1764297901\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法简单却充满回报。你需要策略性地放置建筑，最大化你的得分——有些建筑物在彼此靠近时表现更好，而有些则需要空间才能繁荣。随着你在积分条上达到新的里程碑，你将解锁新的建筑包，让游戏体验保持新鲜感和兴奋感。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/3688eed734524654094eded89042fbfb.poster.avif?t=1764297901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/3688eed734524654094eded89042fbfb.webm?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/3688eed734524654094eded89042fbfb.mp4?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/7a62d8adef56e10952dcc42219e18a1b.avif?t=1764297901\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《桃花源物语：建造小镇》，一个充满魅力的村庄岛屿！在这里你能够体验到轻松又有趣的消遣方式。在建造可爱的小岛社区的同时解压。无论你是经验丰富的玩家，还是只是想寻找一种轻松的方式度过时间，这款游戏轻松的氛围和简单的操作都能让你快速上手并享受其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.poster.avif?t=1764297901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.webm?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.mp4?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/4d21f141bc638a9ad088dc93462c19ff.avif?t=1764297901\" width=616 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏提供了策略与拼图相结合的城市建造乐趣，你能够在各色各样的场景中自由的创造，雪原、炙热沙漠、翠绿草原、巍峨山脉和茂密森林都有属于你的世外桃源。随着你的村庄在地图上不断扩展，每完成一关时，你会进入更大、更复杂的地图。游戏中的动态天气和昼夜循环增加了沉浸感，让你的村庄充满生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/b3ff1741c65da12a277d664ec4466148.poster.avif?t=1764297901\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/b3ff1741c65da12a277d664ec4466148.webm?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/b3ff1741c65da12a277d664ec4466148.mp4?t=1764297901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好踏上一段放松的村庄建设旅程吧，每一个决策都会塑造你的小世界。一起来体验这款游戏带来的欢乐与宁静。祝你建造愉快！</p>",
